Post Lightning Dashboards to Slack
You can share analytics with colleagues across your Slack workspaces and channels.
Required editions: Essentials, Group (View Only), Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, Developer Editions
Permissions needed: Connect Salesforce with Slack

To set up Post to Slack:
- In Setup, enter Slack and select Slack Apps Setup
- Select CRM Analytics for Slack and agree to the Terms and Conditions
- Add CRM Analytics for Slack to your personal Slack sidebar and connect your Salesforce account

After setup, a Post to Slack icon appears on Lightning dashboards. Click the icon to share the dashboard in selected Slack channels.
The post includes a link to view the dashboard in Salesforce or click View Details to see more actions.
